comments.body:
The `Remap*` keys were deprecated with commit https://github.com/containers/podman/commit/f6a50311c56d motivated by https://github.com/containers/podman/issues/17984.

I do not see a direct counterpart for `--uidmap` in the Quadlet docs but the code seems to support a "manual" mode which in turn isn't documented in podman-create.  All very confusing!  It seems though that the "auto" mode allows for specifying custom gid and uid mappings.

@giuseppe may be able to help my confusion.
